com.github.protobufel.el

Class BuilderELResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.el.ELResolver
      • com.github.protobufel.el.BuilderELResolver
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MessageELResolver

    public class BuilderELResolver
extends javax.el.ELResolver
    ProtoBuf Builder ELResolver, like MapELResolver with field name or FieldDescriptor as a key.
    • the field can be either a String, or a FieldDescriptor
    • getValue(javax.el.ELContext, java.lang.Object, java.lang.Object) returns a special wrapper for the repeated field, either IRepeatedFieldValueBuilder for a primitive field, or IRepeatedFieldMessageBuilder for a Message type field; and delegates to the underlying Message.Builder in case of a singular field
    • setValue(javax.el.ELContext, java.lang.Object, java.lang.Object, java.lang.Object) delegates to to the underlying Message.Builder
    See Also:
    ProtoLists, MapELResolver, ELResolver
